                            <comment id="14650489" author="githubbot" created="Sat, 1 Aug 2015 18:12:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user sachingoel0101 commented on the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/971#issuecomment-126943148&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/971#issuecomment-126943148&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    @mxm, you should verify if should we do away with the logging test since you reviewed it.&lt;br/&gt;
    If not, the problem is easily fixed by setting a free port instead of always using the default port.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14651054" author="githubbot" created="Sun, 2 Aug 2015 15:35:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user StephanEwen commented on the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

