&lt;p&gt;    This looks good, thanks you!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    One followup issue: The flag to suppress the logging is `&lt;del&gt;q` or `&lt;/del&gt;&lt;del&gt;sysoutLogging`. The long version seems inconsistent with &quot;q&quot;. It should probably be called `&lt;/del&gt;-quiet`.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
